1010701.name: Osiris's Return
1010701.desc: After a long period of recuperation, Overture Squad member Osiris has returned.

1020501.name: AGI Mecha Rebellion
1020501.desc: The self-righteous chairman of Spealght Industries, Eugene, surrounded by his own rebelling AGI Mecha.

1020101.name: AGI Mecha Crisis
1020101.desc: The AGI Mecha Crisis that broke out three years ago has already faded from people's memories.

1010601.name: Bound Asura
1010601.desc: Asura bound in a factory's underground workshop.

1020301.name: Ethan Enters the Fight
1020301.desc: Ethan, the leader of the Children of Iron, appears before a crowd.

1030901.name: Secret Investigation
1030901.desc: Hiding in the shadows, Baldr eavesdrops on Ethan and Halphas's conversation, however...

1040301.name: Winter Squad Standing By
1040301.desc: The Winter Squad prepares to head out after receiving a request for help.

1040401.name: Tied-Up Eugene
1040401.desc: The Overture Squad finds Eugene tied up in the manufacturing room.

1050301.name: Into the Source Layer
1050301.desc: The crazed Halphas drags the Overture Squad into its home ground—the Source Layer.

1050401.name: Ausar Enters the Fight
1050401.desc: Once in the Source Layer, Osiris—no longer able to suppress her second personality—transforms into Ausar.

1050501.name: Form Removal
1050501.desc: Osiris uses her strong willpower to lift the Ausar form.

1051201.name: Attack
1051201.desc: At the last minute, Novich—his cover blown—takes advantage of the chaos to attack Baldr before making his escape.

1060101.name: Legends of Sasanami - The Five Mountain Gods
1060101.desc: Izuru, Karasugo, Miyahebi, Sanzaru, and Akishika—Over 200 years ago, these five mountain gods watched over Sasanami.

1060102.name: The Mountain Deities' Wrath
1060102.desc: Later, humans angered the mountain gods and they continued to rain down disasters upon them.

1060103.name: Journey to Madoiyama
1060103.desc: The Child of Heaven and five clerics went to Madoiyama and conducted a ritual for the mountain deities.

1060104.name: The Order of the Five Families
1060104.desc: Once the mountain gods' fury was quelled, they became the five families and established Sasanami's new structure.

1060105.name: Dark Clouds
1060105.desc: Times change, and at present, the Izuru family is power and Sasanami District is in the shadow of a dark cloud of assassinations.

1060401.name: Playing Go
1060401.desc: Miyahebi Syuu plays weiqi with Izuru Masayoshi in the master room of his home, each move containing hidden gems.

1061101.name: Serpentine Shadow Under the Moon
1061101.desc: Kuninotokotachi encounters Orochi on her way to meet up with Buzenbo.

1070101.name: Haughty Visitor
1070101.desc: A rather proud and haughty guest appears at Aether Gazer—Hera from the Omorfies District.

1070301.name: Buzenbo and the Inner Demon
1070301.desc: An inner demon born in a maze and embodying Buzenbo's dark side, it wields words as weapons in its ceaseless assault on Buzenbo's weak points.

1070501.name: The Painted World
1070501.desc: After defeating the Monk, Tsukuyomi and Buzenbo are disturbed by what they see in the paintings and enter the illusion known as The Painted World.

1071001.name: The Girl Who Forfeited Her Life
1071001.desc: Hera lifts her hands as she prepares to attack The General with fire, when the girl beside The General steps in front of him to protect him.

1080101.name: Games of the Past
1080101.desc: A beautiful scene from Miyahebi Family's life can be glimpsed in the illusion of the painting.

1080601.name: Cruel Memory
1080601.desc: In the memory illusion, Tsukuyomi and Buzenbo see the profound remorse Takenaka Hiromoto feels after being unable to save Aya.

1080602.name: Lost Family Crest
1080602.desc: Buzenbo and Tsukuyomi see a Karasugo crest amid the fire and flames, indicating that the incident at the Miyahebi home four years ago is more complicated than it appears.

1080701.name: The Monk's Liberation
1080701.desc: After a heated battle, the Monk is finally liberated from his deep-seated self-doubt and anguish.

1081001.name: Burning Test Bed
1081001.desc: Facing the Visbanes' fusion test bed, the indignant Hera takes it upon herself to destroy the equipment with fire.

1081101.name: Kurimoto Aoi and Miyahebi Syuu
1081101.desc: In a memory, Kurimoto Aoi expresses her heartfelt thanks to Miyahebi Syuu for entrusting her with the ceremonial mission.

1090501.name: Their Own Decisions
1090501.desc: To stop Miyahebi Aya from rattling Miyahebi Syuu's determination to capture Sasanami, The Strategist wraps his fingers tightly around her throat.

1090801.name: The Snake God Appears
1090801.desc: The snake god finally appears in her true form before the Modifiers.

1130201.name: Novich's Intel
1130201.desc: Aether Gazer confirms that some faction is after the Sephirah Core. Meanwhile, Novich has reportedly been sighted in multiple locations.

1130401.name: Into the Dream
1130401.desc: Hades has everyone sit by Oneiroi's side, and with the sound of that soft, sweet voice, they all enter Ron's dream...

1130701.name: Sword & Cello

1130801.name: Athena's Memory 1
1130801.desc: During the internal competition to elect the Convallaria Commander, Athena defeats her own elder brother, Argo, and calls him out for cheating.

1131501.name: Ron Gets Caught

1131601.desc: The bewitched Ron gives his body over to Ladon so he can use it to confront Athena.

1131701.desc: Seeing the art pieces that she vows to protect are all destroyed by Visbanes, Athena's heart gradually crumbles amid these fires of cruelty.

1131702.name: Medusa
1131702.desc: Under Ladon's control, Ron lifts up the mirror. It reflects the light cast by the precious jewels set in the statue, and a portal to the Source Layer opens up in mid-air.

1131901.name: The Down-and-Out Commander
1131901.desc: When Hera and the others arrive, they see a lone Athena, on her knees and leaning on her sword, in the middle of the ruins of the temple.

1131902.name: Athena's Memory 2
1131902.desc: A 9-year-old Athena kneels beside her grandmother, listening intently to her teachings.

1140101.name: Ladon in the Mirror
1140101.desc: Ron is at the library preparing for an exam when a bronze mirror falls off a bookshelf and hits him. Picking up the mirror, he discovers that a person who calls himself Ladon is trapped within it.

1140102.name: Ladon in the Mirror
1140102.desc: Ron is at the library preparing for an exam when a bronze mirror falls off a bookshelf and hits him. Picking up the mirror, he discovers that a person who calls himself Ladon is trapped within it.

1141102.name: Scythe Waver
1141102.desc: While exploring the Omorfies Source Layer, Scythe Waver suddenly appear and block the way.

1141302.name: Comrades

1141401.name: The Farce Ends
1141401.desc: Hades, Enlil, Mintha, and Leuce defeat the Visbanes disguised as dancers, putting an end to the chaos of the gala.

1141501.name: Shadow Attack
1141501.desc: While on his way to check the situation at the gala, Oceanus is attacked by Novich, who has been lurking in the shadows.

1141503.name: Shadow Attack
1141503.desc: While on his way to check the situation at the gala, Oceanus is attacked by Novich, who has been lurking in the shadows.

1141502.name: Self-Awareness
1141502.desc: Realizing that he'd only attacked Oceanus' avatar, Novich whirls around, only to find Oceanus and several more avatars waiting behind him.

1141601.name: Oneiroi Awakens
1141601.desc: To save everyone, Oneiroi unleashes the power of dreams, routing the surrounding Visbanes.

1141701.name: Ladon's Shadow
1141701.desc: Ladon unfurls his massive dragon wings in front of the astonished crowd, revealing his true form.

1141901.name: Prelude to Change
1141901.desc: At the lectern, Hades announces her decision of major reforms through live streaming.

1160201.name: Zenkibo on Sickbed
1160201.desc: Being attacked and injured, Zenkibo lies on sickbed, murmuring painfully in dream.

1160202.name: Returning Two
1160202.desc: Due to the successive attacks on the Modifiers, Odin and Thor urgently return from Xu Heng to Aether Gazer.

1160301.name: Wounded Skuld
1160301.desc: Wounded Skuld sits in a corner of an alley in Ain Soph late at night.

1160801.name: Non-existent Photo
1160801.desc: In the healing room, the Administrator and Skuld have a good time and take a souvenir photo.

1160901.name: The Blackbird and the Tower
1160901.desc: The bird looks down over the mortal realm below the tower. Its feathers, shifting like ink blots diffusing on paper, stretch down from the sky. It seems to be looking for something—

1160902.name: Thor's Outburst
1160902.desc: Pushing the door of the conference room to find Shu fall to the ground, badly injured, and Thor raising his hammer with the intention of hitting Shu.

1161501.desc: During the search outside, Heimdall, whose memory has been tampered by an unknown force, suddenly turns her attack on Ookuninushi.

1161601.name: Camera & Lover

1161701.desc: With her grip on the seat and her shrieks mixed with the voices of other tourists on the boat, Skuld looks like a perfectly ordinary teenage girl.

1161901.name: Ferris Wheel of Fright
1161901.desc: The Ferris wheel stops abruptly at its highest point, and in front of the Administrator and Skuld is Death of Fear, armed with a giant hammer.

1162101.name: Uld's Debut
1162101.desc: The culprit behind the series of incidents—0704 Uld, comes out from the fog.

1162901.name: Déjà Vu

1162902.name: Déjà Vu

1163101.name: White Valkyrie

1163102.name: Return of Memory
1163102.desc: The young girl walks back to the beginning of her memories amidst a sky of petals and bright white light.

1163901.name: Power of Memory
1163901.desc: An emblem appears in the boy's eyes, a symbol of the power he has unleashed. However, when facing the girl in front of him, the effect of this power seems to be unexpected.

1164201.desc: Without noticing, Paracaesar, who's speaking eloquently, is choked on the neck and lifted into mid-air by Odin.

1204101.desc: Mengzhang and Jianbing, who are messing around in the Tian Lu Traders, accidentally break one of Luliang's jade vases.

1204201.name: Murmur in Dream
1204201.desc: In a vague dream, Ver hears someone's murmur.

1204302.desc: On Chang'an Bridge in Yu Jing, Xu Heng, Ver and Gengchen discuss the identity and duties of the Modifiers.

1204401.name: The One with the Longest Company
1204401.desc: Ver and the Administrator spend a happy day at tourist attractions.

1204501.name: Crystal Cloud Dragons
1204501.desc: Gengchen gives a pair of jade pendants she made to Ver and the Administrator as a goodbye gift.

1210401.desc: Gengchen uses her Access Key to seal the Cinders. The two agree that Gengchen will look after the Cinders until Odin finds a way to transport them.

1214101.name: The Final Dream
1214101.desc: At the broken end of the world, Gremory falls into chaos.

1214301.name: The Mountain
1214301.desc: Upon receiving an urgent message from Yingzhao, Luliang immediately rushes to Mount Jingdu.

1214401.name: Shattered Power
1214401.desc: Lingguang inspects Gengchen and discovers Gengchen's Prime Power has been further weakened from helping Odin collect the Cinders.

1214601.desc: While marking the graves of Xu Heng's victims, we observe a moment of silence in front of the tombs.

1214801.desc: Jianbing is trapped by Novich inside a space full of Visbanes, left to fight his way back out.

1215101.name: The Second Shadow

1215201.name: A Night Falls Red

1215301.name: Yu Jing Front Line
1215301.desc: Luliang commands a crew of helpers to resist the Visbanes with all their might.

1215401.name: Silent Goodbye
1215401.desc: When Luliang seeks proof, she is faced with the cruel reality. But there is no time now for tears.

1215402.name: Astral Engine (Night)
1215402.desc: The culmination of Xu Heng's top gravity technology, which is incredible no matter how many times you see it.

1215501.name: One-Way Crossroads
1215501.desc: Odin notices something is wrong with Gengchen and comes to stop her.

1215502.desc: I saw civilization up in flames, with no chance for reboots or rebuilding.

1215503.name: Ragnarök
1215503.desc: Everyone I know died, one by one, and I mean really dying, with no right to enter the Cycle.

1215504.name: Horrifying Shadow
1215504.desc: The scale's fully tipped over. And all resistance torn asunder...

1215506.name: One-Way Crossroads
1215506.desc: Odin notices something is wrong with Gengchen and comes to stop her.

1215601.name: A Wordless Victory
1215601.desc: Gengchen and Odin stand back to back. Even though they disagree, the two have never parted ways.

1220101.name: Sprouting Heart
1220101.desc: Strange and painful memories flood my mind...

1220301.name: Sisters Together
1220301.desc: Inside, Linyu and Yingzhao fight together seamlessly to take out the Visbanes.

1220401.name: Sky Patrol (Rift)

1220501.desc: The culmination of Xu Heng's top gravity technology, which is incredible no matter how many times you see it.

1220502.name: Sky Patrol (Set)
1220502.desc: From the hills behind the Quad, a beam of light of black and white, formed of endless Divine Power, shoots toward the rift. A dragon's roar echoes over the city and then, for a moment, everything falls silent.

1220503.name: Stabilizing the Earth
1220503.desc: Thrusting Gungnir into the earth, Odin uses Divine Power to stabilize Xu Heng's ley lines.

1221001.name: First Encounter
1221001.desc: Long ago, a strange yet familiar girl pulled me up from the Source Layer.

1221101.name: A Long-Awaited Reunion
1221101.desc: Promise... This simple song name reminds me of the song the girl softly hummed.

1221201.name: Rebellion (Return)
1221201.desc: "Okay, let's go. And see what's waiting for us."

1221301.name: Weakling's Will
1221301.desc: The shield is shattered, the sword is broken. But...

1221302.name: Keeping the Oath
1221302.desc: "I can't protect Admin unless I get stronger."

1221401.name: Closed Heart
1221401.desc: Strange and painful memories flood my mind...

1221402.name: Rebellion (Indecision)
1221402.desc: "Yes. I have to get Admin out."

1224401.desc: Inside the Astral Engine, Turing observes Mengzhang and forces him to disable the defense program.

1224801.name: Quiet Imbalance
1224801.desc: Turing and Gengchen face off in the control room.

1224901.name: Wandering Thoughts
1224901.desc: At the junction of eras and the origin of time, Turing ponders the meaning of the world.

1225101.desc: Gengchen unseals the Sephirah Core, releasing inky blots into the air and triggering a heated battle.

1225201.name: Ultimatum
1225201.desc: Odin single-handedly unleashes a powerful attack on thousands of opponents.

1225202.name: Odin's Fury
1225202.desc: The sharpened spear leaves behind nothing but the Visbanes' anguished cries.

1225401.name: On Thin Ice
1225401.desc: In Aether Gazer's fine restaurant, Odin, Paracaesar, and Red Fox begin a discussion.

1230101.name: Forest Altar

1230102.name: Trilateral Talks
1230102.desc: The Karasugo, Akishika, and Izuru families discuss how they'll respond to the Night Parade of the Beasts.

1230103.desc: The Karasugo, Akishika, and Izuru families discuss how they'll respond to the Night Parade of the Beasts.

1230104.name: The Lioness of CORG
1230104.desc: Our guest has made herself comfortable in a seat clearly not intended for guests. She stretches, reminding me of a lioness settling down to enjoy the sun.

1230301.name: Ninkyoumon
1230301.desc: A bone-chilling wind rises from the forest, and a valiant figure appears before the Administrator.

1230501.name: The Head of the Akishikas
1230501.desc: A warrior woman in military attire greets us.

1230801.name: The Legend of the Deer God
1230801.desc: The old man gives a lively telling of the legend of the Deer God.

1231201.desc: A cold wind rises, leaving a frost on every surface. Ninkyoumon is about to teach her opponents a lesson about the laws of Shimogyou District.

1234401.desc: The statue collapses in an instant. The majesty of the god has disappeared.

1234601.desc: Sekhmet's face appears in front of me upside down. She's come up with a crazy plan.

1234801.desc: When she thinks of when they first met, Kuramitsuha always remembers the fireworks exploding across the Shimogyou sky.

1235101.name: Preacher of Lies
1235101.desc: Lady Akishika is placed on this altar. It's as if she is there as a sacrifice.

1235201.name: Night Parade of the Beasts
1235201.desc: The Deer God has appeared, on top of a wall that should be unclimbable, gazing down on the people below as they scurry to safety.

1235301.desc: Akishika Himiko uses herself as the tinder to start the fire that would burn out the evil gods.

1235401.desc: She's still persona non grata with the locals, and now there's even fewer people willing to be with her.

3170301.desc: Sekhmet draws up a profile on the Crow God in her mind.

3170501.name: Girl from the Alter-dimension
3170501.desc: From within the infinite alter-dimension, the girl quietly watches me.

3170701.desc: Sekhmet's theory now verified, she and Kuninotokotachi respond together to the sudden appearance of Crow God servants.

3171201.desc: Senba crouches on the ground hugging her knees, her emotions churning in her head.

3171501.desc: Senba turns to walk toward the portal, reluctantly bidding me farewell.

3171701.desc: Tsukuyomi has been trapped for ages, repeating a grueling battle all day long. Still, she remains calm.

3172901.desc: Even if it's overwritten by the Crow God's memetic abilities, "humanity" will still press on, determined to meet its own death head on.

3181301.desc: Faced with an invasion of the Snake God's Bane Energy into her body, Buzenbo cuts open her arm with her Access Key and pours Divine Grace over the wound.

3181901.name: The City's Determination
3181901.desc: Karasugo Sendou and Kagutsuchi prepare to meet the Imperial Army in battle before the Shimogyou city walls, determined to never back down.

3181902.name: From Shimogyou
3181902.desc: Kuramitsuha makes it to the Shimogyou battle in the nick of time, and frost sweeps over the battlefield.

3182201.name: Looking Back and Moving Forward
3182201.desc: With a great battle just ahead of them, Sekhmet and the Administrator get into a discussion about gods and humanity.

3182202.name: Looking Back and Moving Forward
3182202.desc: With a great battle just ahead of them, Sekhmet and the Administrator get into a discussion about gods and humanity.

3182301.name: walking together
3182301.desc: Clumsy as her efforts are, Ningishzida succeeds in bolstering the CORG agents' morale.

3182401.name: At the Banquet
3182401.desc: At this insidious banquet, a wicked plot is gradually bubbling to the surface.

3182501.name: Ambition on Display
3182501.desc: A grand scheme in motion, the Izuru Lord's words no longer conceal his ambition.

3182601.name: Serving as a Seal
3182601.desc: The light emitting from the Yata no Shinkyou neutralizes the force exerted by Akika.

3182701.name: Defying the Gods
3182701.desc: Under Karasugo Sendou's leadership, the people of Sasanami embark on their crusade against the gods.

3182801.name: Rallying the Pheasant Squad
3182801.desc: The members of the Pheasant Squad assemble before the powerful Akika.

3182802.name: The Power of Humanity
3182802.desc: Remembering humanity's courage, Sekhmet activates her Omega gear at the critical moment.

3190001.name: Tarina
3190001.desc: The osmanthus flowers outside the window are wet with rain. Tarina hums a tune.

3193401.name: Boss of Land of Moons
3193401.desc: Thoth, dressed in civvies, says hello to Ver on the street.

3194601.name: Afternoon Respite
3194601.desc: On the busy street, the girls are enjoying their afternoon tea.

3195001.name: Hello, Ver
3195001.desc: Looking at her weak and cowardly self from the past, Ver gives her a gentle hug with mixed feelings.

3190901.name: Night at the Beach
3190901.desc: The two of them have the stars and the beach to themselves. The Prez tells a story from the past.

3196501.name: Not Alone
3196501.desc: Ningishzida, with a grin from ear to ear, rushes over and gives Ver a big hug.

3197601.name: So Far Away
3197601.desc: As she looks at the prayer plaque ornament given to her by Admin, Ver's pupils gradually gleam with the moonlight of longing.

3197701.name: Night Owls
3197701.desc: On the rooftop, at night. Ver and Lokken get to talking about their wishes.

3198001.name: Up in Smoke
3198001.desc: Ningishzida looks at everyone tenderly as the pure white fragments peel away and as her life is withering.

3198501.name: Fading
3198501.desc: Something's wrong with the data, and buildings like those on the Plane Layer have appeared in the streets.

3198801.name: Eclipse
3198801.desc: The silver streaks through the night. Chillingly, Thoth has her blade pointed at Ver.

3199301.name: Heart
3199301.desc: Under the osmanthus tree, the air is filled with the fragrance of its blooms. Tarina and Ver hold each other's hands tightly.

3192701.name: Judgment in the Dim
3192701.desc: Sword and armor. Enlightenment and rebirth. The new Ver emerges amidst the black smoke of gunpowder.

3199701.name: A New Agreement
3199701.desc: Their hands, clasped together, are a silent yet profound promise.

2105911.name: The Girl's Hero
2105911.desc:
Faced with a girl crying because she can't see a "hero", Apollo gently tells her:
A hero will definitely appear.

2108401.name: Wake Up
2108401.desc: The Administrator awakes from a coma to see two unfamiliar faces.

2108402.name: Welcome Aboard!
2108402.desc: The confused Admin enters the restaurant, only to discover a lavish welcome feast and everyone from Aether Gazer there waiting.

2106601.name: BunBun-0
2106601.desc: After taking care of a series of incidences, Ookuninushi is leading the way home when she suddenly turns her head and somewhat sheepishly thanks the Administrator.

2103801.name: Dream-Weaving Elf
2103801.desc: Hera makes a gorgeous entrance for the grand finale of her "Kingdom of Dreams" fashion show wearing an outfit she designed herself.

2103901.name: Aquarium Trip
2103901.desc: Clutching the toy dolphin the Administrator gave her, Poseidon is thrilled by the dolphins she sees in the aquarium.

2104801.name: A "Prank"
2104801.desc: Her prank a failure and caught in the living room, Zenkibo believes that punishment awaits her as always. Unexpectedly, what actually awaits her are Arrival Day wishes from everyone.

2103701.name: Eye on the Prize
2103701.desc: Realizing that she's always helping everyone else in the areas she excels in, Hodur finally lets go and lands a gorgeous bullseye.

2102601.name: Saving the Kitty
2102601.desc: The kidnapping crisis resolved, Nuadha dismantles the weapon parts of value and significance before him, directing his focus towards repairing the mechanical kitten that was just wounded while saving him and the Administrator.

2101901.name: A Cup of Coffee, Miss Shu?
2101901.desc: The Administrator who had worked to unburden Miss Shu and become her assistant, in the end, also gains her trust.

2102401.name: The Jackal's Rest
2102401.desc: To force Anubis to stop working, the Administrator marches him to a coffee shop and commands him to sit and rest.

2103301.name: Dream Dash
2103301.desc: "Let's cheer for Golden Current together, Administrator!"

2109901.name: Playing Go
2109901.desc: The game of Go that had been paused several days ago resumes. As the game progresses, Tsukuyomi reveals a rare smile...

2102801.name: Thunder Signal
2102801.desc: To search for Apollo and Zenkibo who are trapped in the center of the storm, Thor raises her Access Key and creates a signal that belongs only to Thunder Squad.

2108001.name: Walking Day
2108001.desc: When Fenrir is found, it's sleeping comfortably in the shade. Vidar, who can't bear to disturb it, sits down on the lawn as well: it is such a peaceful and cozy afternoon suitable for a walk.

2109601.name: Being Taken Care of by the Patient
2109601.desc: The Administrator, who came to visit the injured Hermes, is instead entertained with peeled apples by her.

2109301.name: Whispering Under the Moon
2109301.desc: The silver-haired ninja in the moonlight doesn't want me to go back just like that...

2106701.name: Wish from a Friend
2106701.desc: Oceanus paints the scene of what the Administrator has in mind attentively and prepares to gift it to the Administrator.

2107001.name: Fall Into a Pit Together
2107001.desc: In the mountain of Xu Heng, the Administrator and Jinwu fall into a pit together. Jinwu takes care of the injured Administrator.

2106801.name: A Smile Bright As The Sun
2106801.desc: Admin makes a sunflower sculpture for Enlil. Enlil is very happy to receive the gift.

2109401.name: Butterfly's Comforting Kiss
2109401.desc: On a gloomy evening, Hel goes to the Admin's room to comfort them after a nightmare.

2109402.name: Butterfly's Comforting Kiss
2109402.desc: The two keep each other company, both feeling concerned for the other. Hel lightly kisses the Admin and keeps watch throughout the night.

2109403.name: Butterfly's Comforting Kiss
2109403.desc: The two keep each other company, both feeling concerned for the other. Hel lightly kisses the Admin and keeps watch throughout the night.

2104201.name: A Gift From Hades
2104201.desc: It seems my destiny has been linked to Hades through this puppet...

2102701.name: Whalesong Healing
2102701.desc: Leviathan, who undid the restrictions on the Access Key to help her Master, excitedly wants to share her happiness with everyone.

2108101.name: Waves of Joy
2108101.desc: Skadi rescues Admin from drowning due to a leg cramp. The two play giddily in the water.

2108102.name: Waves of Joy
2108102.desc: Skadi rescues Admin from drowning due to a leg cramp. The two play giddily in the water.

2109902.name: Hot Spring Reflection
2109902.desc: Tsukuyomi's steamy breath hangs densely over the hot spring, proof of the mutual trust between her and the Admin.

2105501.name: Sunshower Prospects
2105501.desc: Admin brings Kuramitsuha up to the tower to get some air. Rain begins to fall from the sunny sky as the two discuss their ideals and the future.

2107501.name: Nature's Echo
2107501.desc: Paperwork to one side, Lingguang lowers her eyes and plucks the strings of her zither. The sound gathers the beauty of nature, then resonates it out to those in her thoughts.

2107502.name: Nature's Echo
2107502.desc: Paperwork to one side, Lingguang lowers her eyes and plucks the strings of her zither. The sound gathers the beauty of nature, then resonates it out to those in her thoughts.

2104802.name: "Prank Pledge"
2104802.desc: After Goki's quiz game, Zenkibo and the Administrator make a vow of mischief.

2104803.name: "Prank Pledge"
2104803.desc: After Goki's quiz game, Zenkibo and the Administrator make a vow of mischief.

2105801.name: Fireworks Dream
2105801.desc: Before launching the firework in his hand into the deep-blue sky, Kagutsuchi makes a small wish to the Administrator.

2105802.name: Fireworks Dream
2105802.desc: Before launching the firework in his hand into the deep-blue sky, Kagutsuchi makes a small wish to the Administrator.

2106602.name: Lingering Morning Thoughts
2106602.desc: Her cheeks flushed from sleep, Ookuninushi gently takes hold of the Administrator's hand.

2106603.name: Lingering Morning Thoughts
2106603.desc: Her cheeks flushed from sleep, Ookuninushi gently takes hold of the Administrator's hand.

2101101.name: Antinomy
2101101.desc: The three discuss the day's events. While lulling Ausar to sleep, the Administrator experiences a minor conflict.

2101102.name: Antinomy
2101102.desc: The three discuss the day's events. While lulling Ausar to sleep, the Administrator experiences a minor conflict.

2101103.name: Antinomy
2101103.desc: The three discuss the day's events. While lulling Ausar to sleep, the Administrator experiences a minor conflict.

2101104.name: Misattribution
2101104.desc: Ausar and Osiris have the same hopeful dream—about the Administrator.

2101105.name: Letter to the Fox
2101105.desc: Her heart pounding, Osiris places an important letter into the hands of the one she admires.

2101106.name: Letter to the Fox
2101106.desc: Her heart pounding, Osiris places an important letter into the hands of the one she admires.

2104101.name: Ride with the Setting Sun
2104101.desc: On horseback with the Administrator, Athena finally realizes how wonderful a moment's respite can be.

2104102.name: Chord of Convallaria
2104102.desc: One quiet evening, Athena picks up her cello again for the Administrator and plays a song about friendship.

2105001.name: Rain in Cicada Season
2105001.desc: In a mountain forest on a summer's day, Buzenbo and the Administrator—shielding themselves from the rain under the leaves—make a solemn promise to meet again.

2105002.name: Rain in Cicada Season
2105002.desc: In a mountain forest on a summer's day, Buzenbo and the Administrator—shielding themselves from the rain under the leaves—make a solemn promise to meet again.

2102702.name: Aim at the Target!
2102702.desc: The Administrator gives the underconfident Leviathan a shooting lesson at the arcade.

2109501.name: Rainy Night
2109501.desc: After a sudden downpour, Thoth, wearing the Administrator's shirt, expresses her feelings by the window.

2109502.name: Rainy Night
2109502.desc: After a sudden downpour, Thoth, wearing the Administrator's shirt, expresses her feelings by the window.

2109503.name: Rainy Night
2109503.desc: After a sudden downpour, Thoth, wearing the Administrator's shirt, expresses her feelings by the window.

2103902.name: As Promised
2103902.desc: In the morning sun, the Admin woke up to meet Poseidon.

2101906.name: Waltz
2101906.desc: In simulated training, Hugh danced a gorgeous and special waltz with the Admin.

2109704.name: The Smell of Baking in the Morning
2109704.desc: Surrounded by the aroma of warm chocolate, Oneiroi hands the Admin a cookie she's baked with love.

30110101.name: Visiting Ausar
30110101.desc: The Administrator arrives in the care unit to see the wreckage as well as the bound Ausar.

30111012.name: Broken Doll
30111012.desc: Osiris awakes in the middle of the night to discover that the doll Verthandi gave her has been ripped in two, and her pet cat is curled up and trembling, looking at her with fear in its eyes.

30111013.name: Barbecue for Two
30111013.desc: Verthandi and Osiris eat dinner at a barbecue restaurant, the former continuously comforting the depressed latter.

30111014.name: Operating Table
30111014.desc: Osiris lies on the operating table and blames herself, thinking her selfish actions will get Ausar killed. As the anesthetic starts to take effect, she slips into unconsciousness with a heart full of remorse.

30111015.name: Special Treatment
30111015.desc: Although Osiris has long struggled to overcome the influence of this other personality, she feels the distance growing between her and her companions.

30111016.name: Imago Room: Solitude
30111016.desc: Osiris finally realizes that her actions before were just her running away and not fully trusting her companions.

30111017.name: Imago Room: Remorse
30111017.desc: Osiris, now aware of her own weakness and avoidance, sheds tears of remorse.

30111019.name: Imago Room: Rise
30111019.desc: To help the Administrator out of the predicament, Osiris decides to face Ausar directly, whom she fears.

30111018.name: Protected Companion
30111018.desc: Osiris steps forward to protect the Administrator from Ausar's attack.

30210101.name: Black Coffin Reaper
30210101.desc: A girl with whitish, silver hair carrying a heavy, black coffin on her shoulders stands amidst the ruins, her hair whipping about in the breeze.

30210401.name: The Psychologist
30210401.desc: A self-proclaimed psychologist dressed casually in black attire with messy hair, the rings around his eyes are visible even under the glasses.

30210601.name: The Butterflies at Grave
30210601.desc: The first glimmers of sunlight suddenly appear ahead like a halo in the darkness of night. The white butterflies hover before a tombstone covered in white flowers.

30211301.name: Crazy Experiment
30211301.desc: In a transparent cage, Vena shuts her eyes as if just going to sleep, while Otis—the one running the experiment—shoots us a contemptuous sneer.

30211601.name: New Family
30211601.desc: Replacing Vena, the girl becomes the newest member of Hel's family.

30211602.name: Shadow of the Past
30211602.desc: Hel still remembers that moment, when Vena extended her hands with a warmth reminiscent of the first rays of the spring sun melting the icy winter's chill.

30211701.name: Valiant Debut
30211701.desc: What are the chances god is a golden-haired girl with mechanical legs?

30212201.name: Determined to Run
30212201.desc: "I'm gonna run with everything I've got!"

30301101.name: Beauty at the Beach
30301101.desc: When my consciousness returned from the darkness of chaos, I saw several familiar faces before me.

30305301.name: Forest Encounter
30305301.desc: Leviathan follows the call emanating from the shrubbery until she arrives before a rock in the center of a clearing—This seems like both a chance encounter... and a long-awaited reunion.

30308101.name: Snowflake 2's Conviction
30308101.desc:
To live up to her conviction that "no crew member will be left behind," Skadi decides to take a chance with her beloved ship.
Beyond the porthole, that massive maelstrom draws ever nearer...

30310101.name: Underwater World
30310101.desc: After entering the bubble world, Skadi marvels at the spectacle that lies before her. She looks up at the watery firmament, seeming to have discovered something...

30311201.name: Siren's Return
30311201.desc: With an all-engulfing storm in tow, the Siren descends once again.

30312201.name: Deep Sea Angel
30312201.desc: A light seems to pierce through the darkness before me, and when I finally open my eyes, Leviathan is reaching her hand out towards me, like an angel from heaven.

30314201.name: Countertide Whalesong
30314201.desc:
Leviathan slowly opens her eyes and is shocked to discover that she can suddenly breathe underwater.
As for the being that was speaking, it's quietly snuggled up in front of her.

30317101.name: Against the Tide
30317101.desc: Leviathan raises the Countertide Whalesong in her hand high in the air—This time, she blocked Siren's way.

30319101.name: Siren's Arrival
30319101.desc: The Siren's appearance sets off a towering tidal wave. From the very top, it loftily looks down at the diminutive survey boat.

30322101.name: In Memory of Summer
30322101.desc: After crawling up from the beach, I press the camera's shutter button to capture a summer's moment worth commemorating.

30322102.name: Deep Blue Encounter
30322102.desc:
"Hey, are you guys my next batch of passengers?"
The young girl sitting on the side of the boat calls out. Her eyes, like this survey boat, are a blue color as deep as the sea.

30422101.name: Caught Off Guard
30422101.desc: Having been flagged as an intruder by the AGI Mecha guard, young Athena runs to hide inside Stellaris Temple.

30423101.name: The Working Artist
30423101.desc: Pushing open the mysterious door, an artist appears before Athena, who’s intently focusing on his sculpture.

30424101.name: Oceanus' Gift
30424101.desc: To remind Ardisis to be punctual, Oceanus presents a personally-crafted pocket watch to the overly-spontaneous artist.

30426101.name: Courageous Confrontation
30426101.desc: Young Athena raises her sword to protect Ardisis and his sculpture, even in the face of unfathomably powerful opposition.

30429101.name: Two Before the Tomb
30429101.desc: Colleen Pallas is sweeping the tomb of Ardisis, when she encounters a mysterious visitor...

30501101.name: Lamp-Lit Plot
30501101.desc: Under the cover of night, Kingu and a mysterious man are chatting in a secret room. Kingu sits beneath the lamp light, with a rebellious and discontented look on his face.

30502101.name: The Helplessness of a Father
30502101.desc: Marduk's expression is stony as he surveys the disordered mess on the battlefield around him, the glow of flames casting red light across his face.

30503101.name: Code Name: Jackal
30503101.desc: The Jackal hides behind a cargo crate to avoid the nearby rebels, using the holographic screen projected by his watch to communicate with someone.

30503201.name: Stealthy Shadow
30503201.desc: Anubis destroys the warehouse in the cargo area, then walks off in style.

30504101.name: Stealthy Silhouette
30504101.desc: Bastet sits atop the vehicle, greeting the "boss" while grinning adorably.

30505201.name: The Dark Metal Menace
30505201.desc: A massive AGI Mecha uses its alloy blades to slice through the cargo crate being used as cover, sending sparks flying in all directions.

30507201.name: Interrogation and Silence
30507201.desc: In the face of Kingu's pointed questioning, the captured Marduk staunchly remains silent.

30508101.name: Drinkery Gathering
30508101.desc: Deep in thought, Anubis is sipping a crafted brew. Beside him, Bastet takes the opportunity to steal a glimpse of his serious and pondering face.

30509101.name: Game of Cards
30509101.desc: Amidst the dark night, the pub is brightly lit. Bastet sits at a card table sipping her wine, with a victorious grin on her face.

30510201.name: Manly Showdown
30510201.desc: In one corner of the ring in the cargo area, Anubis is tired but happy. Across from him, the King of the Ring sits exhausted on the mat, resigned yet relieved.

30511101.name: Old Record
30511101.desc: A jukebox plays in the dim lamplight. The spinning record appears a bit worn out as it reflects the faces of Anubis and Bastet.

30513101.name: Project Graytower
30513101.desc: Inside the capacious circular laboratory, Marduk recounts his memories of Project Graytower as a large incubation tank emits an eerie fluorescence.

30515101.name: Copper Duel
30515101.desc: The conflict is no longer solvable with words. Kingu initiates a challenge to Marduk that the Rostach bounty hunter could not refuse: a Copper Duel.

30515201.name: Loss and Victory
30515201.desc: Anubis tries to put himself between Marduk and Kingu, yet Kingu remains in his attack stance.

30520101.name: The Fury of a Father
30520101.desc: To protect his son, Marduk defeats Dark Metal through sheer force of will—but he is badly wounded in the process.

30520102.name: Father and Son
30520102.desc: Before Kingu stands the father he resists for so long, but whose plight he finally understands. Behind him lies only the vast night that goes nowhere.

30521201.name: Easy Assault
30521201.desc: Sobek handily takes out the guard soldiers and bursts into the secret warehouse.

30523201.name: The Life of a Bounty Hunter
30523201.desc: Having nearly been captured due to recklessness, Sobek is saved by timely help from Ethan and Olheim.

30525101.name: The Experiment Continues
30525101.desc: Standing in front of the communication screen, a smile emerges on Paracaesar’s face.

30528101.name: Time and Flame
30528101.desc: Hera uses the Phantasmal Dawn Access Key to suspend time and freeze the wave of flame from the explosion.

30529101.name: All Alone
30529101.desc: In a remote corner of a secluded neighborhood, Chloe sits alone in the rain, her back against the wall.

30530101.name: Childhood Joy
30530101.desc: As a child, Chloe and her father, Clement, would sit side by side under the eaves and look up at the stars.

30640101.name: Spring Gift
30640101.desc: Jinwu is happily sitting in the middle of a pile of gifts with his back against a giant Mimir doll. What made Jinwu's smile instantly freeze is the fallen...

30640102.name: Spring Gift
30640102.desc: Jinwu is happily sitting in the middle of a pile of gifts with his back against a giant Mimir doll. What made Jinwu's smile instantly freeze is the fallen...

30640201.name: Reunion Dinner
30640201.desc: The most important part of the New Year's Awakening is of course the sumptuous reunion dinner!

30670101.name: End of the Farce
30670101.desc: Facing the strong enemy, Shu and Hera unleash the Second Access Key to end the farce.

30670102.name: Lamp of Enlightenment
30670102.desc: Heimdall manipulates her wheels in an attempt to create a passageway that will allow her to leave the Theater of Illusion.

30701101.name: Hot News
30701101.desc: Hot news from Ain Soph is playing on TV.

30702201.name: The Man with Firebrand in Hand
30702201.desc: A sudden burst of flame instantly wipes out most of the Visbanes surrounding Heimdall, and the man who harnessed that flame stands in front.

30704101.name: Dialog in front of Tyrfing
30704101.desc: Learning of Tyr's awakening, the old butler hands over Tyrfing to him, the Access Key formerly belonged to Tyr, which he had kept in his custody.

30706201.name: Flaming Beast
30706201.desc: Garmr, an evil beast that raises its head and roars in fire.

30708101.name: Light of the Storeroom
30708101.desc: The yellowish light of the storeroom illuminates the memories of the three as they sort through the items salvaged from the fire.

30712101.name: Flames No Longer Sealed
30712101.desc: In the burning mansion, Tyr unleashes the Bane Energy sealed in his right arm, surrounded by flame and ready to take on the flaming Visbane Garmr.

30712201.name: Recognition of the Tyrfing
30712201.desc: The shadow of Eirikr, standing on the other side of the Tyrfing, silently watches Tyr.

30713201.name: Historic Meeting
30713201.desc: The two giants sit at opposite ends of a long table, negotiating politely yet tactfully.

30801101.name: Gengchen and Lingguang
30801101.desc: News reports claim that the president of Tian Lu Traders has resigned. Lingguang senses Gengchen's agitation and asks her if she wants to go see her old friend.

30801102.name: Recalling the Past
30801102.desc: In the past, Luliang and Gengchen would wine and dine together in Xu Heng's restaurants.

30804101.name: Reunion
30804101.desc: Luliang orders more food than one person can eat, then addresses Gengchen, who has been following her, and invites her to join.

30806101.name: Along the Luo River
30806101.desc: Standing in front of Luliang's gift, "Along the Luo River," Gengchen feels incredibly moved.

30807101.name: Luliang's Return
30807101.desc: After exchanging ideas with Gengchen, Luliang returns to Tian Lu Traders and announces her new plans to reform the company.

30901101.name: The Meeting Adjourns
30901101.desc: Someone gives a shout upon seeing Yingzhao emerge and the crowd rushes toward her.

30904201.name: Looking for Hibiscus
30904201.desc: Jinwu picks a few hibiscus flowers to cheer up the dispirited Yingzhao.

30908101.name: Mining Road Standoff
30908101.desc: Representing Tian Lu Traders, Yingzhao confronts Shoumo in the mine.

30910101.name: Forest Talk
30910101.desc: Deep in the forest, Mengzhang visits Xihe, searching for a way to turn the tables.

31001101.name: Show of Strength
31001101.desc: Upon first arriving in Shashvat, Luwu is robbed by members of a local gang.

31007101.name: A Determined Mind
31007101.desc: Before the hustle and bustle of the race track, Luwu tells Kumar about her commitment to justice.

31008101.name: Picking a Fight
31008101.desc: In a market in Shashvat, Ravana's gaze is full of animosity.

31009101.name: Rules of Rescue
31009101.desc: Determined to go to the pharmaceutical facility, Luwu gets into an argument with Baize over differing ideas.

31011101.name: Luwu's Spear
31011101.desc: The determined Luwu reveals her true power as nine spears of light circle around behind her.

31012201.name: Kali to the Rescue
31012201.desc: Kali, the leader of the Meruism Modifiers, comes to the facility to aid Luwu and Marduk.

31013101.name: Carrying out Justice
31013101.desc: "You are being charged with the following..." Baize flashes her badge at Seema.

31014101.name: Ordinary Departure
31014101.desc: At the Quad, Gengchen sends Zhiming to Shashvat to borrow "The Book of All Past" from Brahmā.

31014201.name: Space of the Past
31014201.desc: As she tracks down Brahmā, Zhiming enters the dataspace of "The Book of All Past."

31020201.name: Confinement
31020201.desc: Outside the locked utility closet, Kumar appears before Zhiming, whose escape attempt failed.

31022101.name: Visitation
31022101.desc: Kumar is imprisoned for attempting to free the drug testers, and argues with Zhiming over differing styles of conduct.

31024101.name: Ethereal Enigma Reboot
31024101.desc: Connected to the computing power extraction system, Zhiming uses the computing power to repair her Access Key Ethereal Enigma.

31025101.name: Zhiming's Shield
31025101.desc: Ethereal Enigma's small shield protects Zhiming, blocking the flames and shock waves created by its bombardment.

31025201.name: Ring of Death
31025201.desc: Ravana's fierce attacks separate Luwu and Kali from their Access Keys and even disperse Zhiming's light beams.

31026101.name: The Storm Settles
31026101.desc: After the Vimoksha Pharma battle, Luwu and Zhiming have some milk tea together on a street in Gharpur.

31111101.name: Just As They've Always Been
31111101.desc: The seasons may come and go, but some people and some things never change.

31102101.name: Flying Towards the Moonlight
31102101.desc: What the girl in the cage desires is to chase the unreachable moonlight.

31102102.name: Companionship
31102102.desc: On a night full of inspiration, Thoth stays up with Ygritte as the latter works hard on her creation.

31101101.name: Secret Handover
31101101.desc: At the restaurant, Thoth entrusts a mysterious girl to Lokken.

31112101.name: Dying Light
31112101.desc: The light of life is about to go out. Thoth and Ygritte gaze at the distant sunset.

31133101.name: The One With No Name
31133101.desc: At the very end, there is nothing more to victory than numbness and nothingness.
